  "name": "Analyze meeting sentiment from Google Meet and send to Salesforce",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from ritik-prog/n8n-automation-templates-5000: Analyze meeting sentiment from Google Meet and send to Salesforce",
  "category": "AI",
  "tags": [
    "n8n 2000 workflows",
